  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Higher model risk drives stricter credibility requirements; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Full 13-factor assessment completed. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: ContextOfUse contains prose description of operating conditions but no structured hasApplicabilityConstraint or hasOperatingEnvelope link, leaving the model's formal range of valid use unspecified (W-ON-02).",
